    "Dr. Peter S. Ruckman": "They show that God is interested in anybody connected with His SON (see p. 37); 2. that the most insignificant people\u2014like those here\u2014get their NAMES in a Book that will be here WHEN HEAVEN AND EARTH HAVE PASSED AWAY. [v_Gen_5_1] Study, especially, the notes on Genesis 5:1 and Matthew 1:1 in the Bible Believer\u2019s Commentary on Genesis (1970) and Matthew (1969). My, what a shock 100,000 \u201cthink tanks\u201d and \u201cbigshots\u201d from history (4000 B.C. to A.D. 3000) will get when they come up before the Last Judgment and find names like those here (\u201cHattush, Elihoenai, Adin, Ebed, Zebadiah, Joab, Jeiel, Bebai,\u201d and later \u201cNymphas, Rufus, Tryphena, Nereus, Asyncritus, and Patrobus\u201d (Rom. 16) standing in a Book that God wrote before [v_Exo_32_32] Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` showed up (Exod. 32:32\u201333); and will be there long after every religion on earth has been annihilated! My, what a traumatic experience! In vain will they look for the names of the most famous and highly publicized people who ever lived; their fellow humans who were \u201cof the world, by the world, for the world,\u201d and against the Holy Spirit: Napoleon, Abraham `[char_Abraham_Exo_17]` Lincoln, Peter `[char_Peter_Mat_4]` the Great, William Glassier, Plato, Aristotle, Einstein, Gandhi, Churchill, Hitler, JFK, Cortez, Balboa, FDR, Caruso, Benny Goodman, Artie Shaw, Beethoven, Somerset Maughm, Mohammed, Ernest Hemingway, Kafka, Marilyn Monroe, Ted and Bobby Kennedy, Arafat, Mandela, M. L. King Jr., General Grant, DeGaulle, Mao Tse-tung, Marx, Lenin, Stalin, and more than 200 \u201cPopes.\u201d My, my, my! What an \u201ceye opener\u201d on \u201cWho\u2019s Who\u201d in God\u2019s sight! God\u2019s Book lists those whom He says are \u201csomebody.\u201d Only occasionally does a king or governor or emperor get mentioned and then only because a JEW (John `[char_John_Ref]` 18\u201319; Acts 27; Exod. 9\u201315) crossed his path. \u201cNot many mighty...not many wise...not many noble\u201d (1 Cor. 1:26). The young men whom I trained here at Pensacola Bible Institute (PBI), between 1964 and 2004, had their names in the [v_Php_4_3] Lamb\u2019s Book of Life (Phil. 4:3, Luke 10:20). By the time \u201cthe books were opened\u201d (Dan. 7; Rev. 20), my young, unknown, unpublicized, unrecognized \u201cRuckmanites\u201d (in a cult!!) will have [v_Rev_20_1] already been reigning on earth with Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ (Rev. 20:1\u20136) for [v_Rev_20_1] 1,000 years (Rev. 20:1\u201310). They are as liable to have their names [v_Exo_32_32] removed from that book (Exod. 32:32; Rev. 3:5) as they are for Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]` Christ to have failed to make a blood atonement for their sins [v_Heb_10_8] (Heb. 10:8\u201312) after God imputed all of their sins to HIM (2 Cor. 5:19). Those are the \u201codds\u201d of any Christian in this age getting his [v_Rom_8_20] name \u201cblotted out\u201d of the Book of Life (see pp. 16\u201319, Rom. 8:20). Perhaps some of our young men slipped through three years of PBI without the New Birth, but the chances are less than one out of",
